<div class="white-space"></div>
<div class="unclassifiable">
  <div class="unclassifiable_banner">
    <h1>#UNCLASSIFIABLE</h1>
    <h6>
      There is something unclassifiable in RENDEZ VOUS IHF, a mystery that is never fully understood:
      Creative or  statutory ? Fun or business ? Casual or sophistication ?
      <br><br>
      The success of RENDEZ VOUS IHF comes from this fundamental ambivalence:
      to present hotels and destinations, to create strategic contacts, to generate ROI, to reinvent itself
      constantly and to live unforgettable experiences and emotions,
      without ever becoming “just” a simple fair of the luxury travel.
    </h6>
  </div>
  <div class="unclassifiable_testimonials">
    <div class="left-testimonial">
      <div class="left-testimonial_avatar">
        <%= image_tag 'testimonial-one.png' %>
      </div>
      <div class="left-testimonial_content">
        <p><i>
          “From the first time I met Alex listening to his principles of RENDEZ VOUS IHF, to the fun of curating a series of unexpected experiences, to the final meaningful delivery – it was very clear to me – this is the new generation of creating emotional connections between people and destinations that will stay memorable. Simply unclassifiable.”
        </i></p>
        <p><b>
          Joachim Hartl, Area General Manager Iberian Peninsula <br> Hilton Worlwide
        </b></p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="right-testimonial">
      <div class="right-testimonial_content">
        <p><i>
          “RENDEZ VOUS IHF Forum's are awesome, funky, unconventional and strikingly different from any other Forums. Alex and Co go out of their way to always surprise us during the networking events and come up with great innovative ideas. <br><br>
          Not only do they truly understand a buyer's needs but they also know how to have the right balance between scheduled appointments and activities. The concept of working in the morning and networking in the afternoon always in a cool unusual place and in a warm atmosphere, is perfect. All social events are always top class with a wow effect with lots of fun and help us all to connect with people on a higher level. Great Event!”
        </i></p>
        <p><b>
         Ulrike Trader, Senior International Events Manager <br> Bird & Bird
        </b></p>
      </div>
      <div class="right-testimonial_avatar">
        <%= image_tag 'testimonial-two.png' %>
