      </div>
      <div class="left-testimonial_content">
        <p><i>
          “RENDEZ VOUS IHF is the bringing together of that which needs no introduction, the expected that becomes the unexpected, a meeting of ideas and beliefs in the luxury travel world that, as Coco Chanel once said, Luxury is the necessity that begins where necessity ends.”
        </i></p>
        <p><b>
          Yuriy Horovyy, Founder & CEO <br> Almont Group
        </b></p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="right-testimonial">
      <div class="right-testimonial_content">
        <p><i>
          “Having participated in several editions of “Rendez-Vous” over the past years, I can say that you guys curate an event like no other!  Both hotel partners and buyers have the opportunity to do business in a relaxed and friendly atmosphere and experience amazingly different things in each destination the event is held in.   Always raising the bar higher!”
