      </div>
      <div class="left-testimonial_content">
        <p><i>
          “RENDEZ VOUS IHF Vienna was a great edition! A right mix between face-to-face meetings with top buyers and unique networking events.
          I would define it as a successful combination of conviviality, professionalism, originality, passion and a pinch of Madness #workhardplayhard "
        </i></p>
        <p><b>
          Anne-Emmanuelle Le Bail, Director of Sales <br>
          Waldorf Astoria and Conrad Hotels & Resorts
        </b></p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="right-testimonial">
      <div class="right-testimonial_content">
        <p><i>
          “Quality networking with the best hotel partners in a creative event.
