      <div class="right-testimonial_avatar">
        <%= image_tag 'testimonial-eight.png' %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="left-testimonial">
      <div class="left-testimonial_avatar">
        <%= image_tag 'testimonial-nine.png' %>
      </div>
      <div class="left-testimonial_content">
        <p><i>
          “My first two rendezvous were fantastic experiences which resulted in great business for the hotel. The intimacy of the event means that you get to feel as though you are part of a family which is amazing.”
        </i></p>
        <p><b>
          Andrew Tabone, International Sales Manager <br> Excelsior Grand Hotel
        </b></p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="right-testimonial">
      <div class="right-testimonial_content">
        <p><i>
          “Materialized business opportunities, first contacts made with decision makers and influencers on both sides of suppliers and buyers and an immediate connection of all the participants thanks to a truly unusual and extremely well designed program.”
        </i></p>
        <p><b>
          Benjamin Caudet, Vice President <br>
          EMEA at ATG Business Travel Management
        </b></p>
      </div>
      <div class="right-testimonial_avatar">
        <%= image_tag 'testimonial-ten.png' %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="left-testimonial">
      <div class="left-testimonial_avatar">
        <%= image_tag 'testimonial-eleven.png' %>
      </div>
      <div class="left-testimonial_content">
        <p><i>
          “RENDEZ VOUS IHF is so different, because Alex and his team manage to find unique locations, unique attractions and deliver a oscar worthy show for an entire weekend. That paired with well qulified buyers makes Rendez-Vous a super event!”
        </i></p>
        <p><b>
          Felix Sigel, Head of Sales <br> 25 hours Hotels
        </b></p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="right-testimonial">
      <div class="right-testimonial_content">
        <p><i>
          “Not only amazing personalities at the RENDEZ VOUS INTERNATIONAL HOTEL FORUM, but also undeniably flexible,
